Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:06.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,It is the turbulent Sengoku period.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:11.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,Warlords keep on fighting day and night over\NJipangu State, where Karakuri people live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:16.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,Karakuri martial artists were sharpening their swords, dreaming of victory and honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:23.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,And now, a wild hero has arrived, seeking to be the number one Karakuri martial artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:27.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi is here-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
